## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources and may not capture the full spectrum of opinions on the topic. Additionally, the perspectives included are primarily from articles and discussions available online, which may not represent the views of all stakeholders, such as educators, students, and publishers. Further research could include empirical studies and surveys to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.